d":2213039,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"落街簽名得唔得？"},{"pid":"6824b023369440e9e00a9698d7435602bcc6ca7c","tid":2213039,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4f2c30490def4a661680566aac199c42a7df8a","tid":2213039,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"XG01咪放link同貼全文啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韋訥亦在備忘錄中寫道：「在目前的新聞報道下，公司決定立即停止主動在社交媒體發文（除了回應客戶有關銀行服務的查詢外），以避免公司的頻道及內容出現負面回應及意見。」<br />\n<br />\n據美國網媒BuzzFeed在20日刊登的報告，稱1999年至2017年期間，一些金融機構被指曾處理合共2萬億美元的可疑交易。當中滙豐被指在2013年9月收到監管機構通知，指當局正調查一宗與旗下戶口有關的龐氏騙局（Ponzi scheme），卻仍繼續為相關帳戶提供服務。"},{"pid":"4e64fceb8648d60adc4ce0d0d21cd6457587a4f9","tid":2213039,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"私生活都管埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f2a360e3ebc369b27ce7780df108b1d6d8b0e9","tid":2213039,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"女teller想兜客都唔得？"},{"pid":"76e4fbe140f8f4ca4f989da68909f7bb7596e82f","tid":2213039,"uid":89198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"支持黨安法都唔得？"},{"pid":"83c4bc28af2405c10fa83512604b0049d97cddd5","tid":2213039,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<br />\n滙豐控股（HSBC，0005）因被指涉及一宗8000萬美元的龐氏騙局（Ponzi scheme）案件的資金流動而陷入風波，美媒22日報道，滙控內部發出備忘錄，要求員工在一段時間內，立即暫停在銀行社交媒體帳戶發文，避免引起負面反應。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社22日報道，指滙控環球商業和投資銀行部門的市場推廣主管韋訥（Tricia Weener）21日向員工發備忘錄。內文稱滙控會暫停於所有社交媒體帳戶發文，直至英國時間22日上午11時為止。<br />\n<br />\n韋訥亦在備忘錄中寫道：「在目前的新聞報道下，公司決定立即停止主動在社交媒體發文（除了回應客戶有關銀行服務的查詢外），以避免公司的頻道及內容出現負面回應及意見。」<br />\n<br />\n據美國網媒BuzzFeed在20日刊登的報告，稱1999年至2017年期間，一些金融機構被指曾處理合共2萬億美元的可疑交易。當中滙豐被指在2013年9月收到監管機構通知，指當局正調查一宗與旗下戶口有關的龐氏騙局（Ponzi scheme），卻仍繼續為相關帳戶提供服務。"},{"pid":"afe7599d27a1d9de5fe7d81aadd0abf5fab26491","tid":2213039,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32155bbf0e165f658b4426173c18bf01ca285cf5","tid":2213039,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"快撚D執笠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1aa1700decfb1ed1243fe22460332fd4ed2bb8","tid":2213039,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"回力標，查黃絲facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb8d276987a4017e9a10a0311ccf1552eef3b25","tid":2213039,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d64a4be79df9cd3fb41fbd0463b337dc08a499a4","tid":2213039,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e64fceb8648d60adc4ce0d0d21cd6457587a4f9","tid":2213039,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"私生活都管埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"應該係講所以匯控嘅官方account都唔可以發文住"},{"pid":"48d7deffb3a8f4c6e9095f0d4204b94b8121c98d","tid":2213039,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4eb8d276987a4017e9a10a0311ccf1552ee